{"tid":2199830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人仲有無人情味？","createTime":"2020-09-12T13:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T13:47:40.000Z","uid":125272,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"56e719fc8202444587112fc0bff257953411a002","tid":2199830,"uid":125272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"話說頭先去左跑步  因為都跑得少少遠<br />\n咁就淨係有帶左電話 身份證 八達通同少少現金<br />\n咁跑完步身水身汗 開始肚餓<br />\n就順便買個飯返屋企食<br />\n個間鋪頭淨係收現金嘅<br />\n咁啱我想食個個飯貴少少<br />\n比我帶嘅現金貴2蚊<br />\n<br />\n我企喺門口望咗一陣<br />\n有個靚女收銀員出嚟問我想食咩<br />\n個餐牌寫明我都照問佢「呢個飯幾錢啊」<br />\n佢答完我我就老實同佢講「哦～我咁啱差2蚊」<br />\n正當我以為佢會話「咁食其他囉」<br />\n點知個靚女好爽快咁答我<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">「由佢啦個2蚊」</span><br />\n我感動到差啲喊出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你見到呢個po<br />\n真係好想同你講  多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我感受到嘅係人情味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ed995752b31bafa482ddf4f9abf766d59a5219","tid":2199830,"uid":125272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"邊個咁快比負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7748f1b45c264104568c0bd0fe2fd51a6d08184f","tid":2199830,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"試過食飯冇帶錢老細話俾我些數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過幫襯左10 幾年"},{"pid":"963702f13de6540423f25bc065277f5bb663e2ae","tid":2199830,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"我就係個收銀<br />\n因為以為你係流浪漢<br />\n所以就收少你兩蚊"},{"pid":"0d52a3312f1c460ff16946066bd98b396e02c68f","tid":2199830,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"其實香港人一直好有人情味<br />\n係連登仔無"}]}